Init:
    dj_arvl_time = arvl_time
    out_time = dj_arvl_time + sys_delay
    out_tbo_adj = -sys_delay
    est_tbo = in_tbo

Dejittering:
    arvl_time_inc = arvl_time - prev_arvl_time
    tp_idx_inc = tp_idx - prev_tp_idx
    in_tpi = arvl_time_inc / tp_idx_inc
    dj_tpi = iir_filter(in_tpi)
    dj_arvl_time += dj_tpi * tp_idx_inc

Prediction:
>   pcr_inc = pcr_time - prev_pcr_time
    tbo_drift = pcr_inc * reg_freq_adj
    est_tbo += tbo_drift

Forward path:
>   in_tbo = pcr_time - dj_arvl_time
    err_tbo = in_tbo - est_tbo
    norm_err_tbo = err_tbo / pcr_inc
    filt_tbo = loop_filter(norm_err_tbo)
    freq_adj = loop_gain * filt_tbo
    reg_freq_adj = clamp(freq_adj)

Delivery time:
    out_inc = pcr_inc - tbo_drift
    out_time += out_inc
    out_tpi = out_inc / pcr_tp_idx_inc

PCR correction:
    out_tbo = est_tbo + out_tbo_adj
    out_pcr = out_time + out_tbo


Non-PCR TP processiong
    tp_idx_inc = tp_idx - prev_tp_idx
    out_time += out_tpi * tp_idx_inc

> : may have wrap around problem!!!

=============================================================

For 1st TP which happens to have PCR:
    dj_arvl_time = arvl_time
    est_tbo = in_tbo = pcr_time - arvl_time
    out_time = dj_arvl_time + sys_delay
             = arvl_time + sys_delay
    out_tbo = est_tbo + out_tbo_adj
            = in_tbo - sys_delay
    out_pcr = out_time + out_tbo
            = arvl_time + sys_delay + in_tbo - sys_delay
            = arvl_time + (pcr_time - arvl_time)
            = pcr_time


If the first PCR is in the n-th TP:
    out_pcr = out_time + out_tbo
            = [arvl_time(0) + sys_delay + n * out_tpi_init]
              + [pcr_time - dj_arvl_time - sys_delay]
            = pcr_time + [arvl_time(0) + n * out_tpi_init - dj_arvl_time] 
            = pcr_time + pcr_adj

pcr_adj is the initial PCR adjustment error introduced by the algorithm.
